abstract: NBA Roundup; Oklahoma City Thunder beats Brooklyn Nets, 110-99; other basketball scores noted.
lead_paragraph: Kevin Durant scored 30 points, and Oklahoma City pulled away in the fourth quarter of a game with frequent lead changes.
